adjectives.description: squirrelproof (comparative more squirrelproof, superlative most squirrelproof)

examples: Although a couple are highly squirrel-resistant—especially the GSP, Mandarin, and Looker SPF—and others can be made squirrel-resistant with the use of baffles, grease, and other barriers, there is no feeder that is squirrelproof all the time.
